    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the 3.8L flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and neutral handling characteristics. The vehicle is mechanically superlative, showing no signs of bore scoring or RMS weeping, with a valvetrain that remains exceptionally quiet. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers over ventilated cross-drilled rotors, maintaining firm pedal pressure and immediate bite. Every bushing, control arm, and damper remains within factory-spec tolerances. This is a rare, concours-level example with a documented service history and a clean DME overrev report.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
